## 2. Ingestion & Scheduled Sync Pipelines (MongoDB → PostgreSQL)
The analytics tools query pre-aggregated, indexed PostgreSQL tables to ensure sub-second response times. Scheduled jobs (handled by `APScheduler` and protected by file-locking concurrency guards) pull and sync live data from the operational MongoDB databases into PostgreSQL.

```mermaid
